The Facebook post promotes the services of the Eurotrans Foundation, focusing on assistance with obtaining Hungarian citizenship. While the timing might be close to the elections, the content itself is not directly related to the parliamentary elections or any specific candidate.  The post does not advocate for or against any candidate or party. The objective is to inform potential clients about the foundation's services, not to influence the vote.  Therefore, it does not meet the criteria for electoral propaganda as defined in Article 36 (7) of LEGE nr. 334 din 17 iulie 2006 and Article 98 t) of LEGE nr. 208 din 20 iulie 2015.
